snippet.textDisplay: Dax you absolute diamond 💯 I love this track man your lyrics hot questions I have had my whole adult life, I would love to believe but I have studied and it's all bullshit to control through fear, the most hate I see coming from any groups are religious ones, anybody I see doing good, anyone who has a heart and soul for other people usually are the most lost, I know this from experience, still it's amazing to see that people all over the world are feeling like me and thinking like me, it means there are serious questions to be answered by those who have the power in the Vatican, those who have toured the planet in history and stolen, killed and eradicated whole cultures and other beliefs that were more spiritual and loving than Christianity, I have for a while now been wanting to visit a church and speak with someone but the very thought of doing so makes me feel strange, I have in my own belief and it doesn't involve scaring people into following anyone's rules, it's common sense to live as the best person you can be towards others and yourself, not money or a great job but how you feel when you walk past the homeless, would you feed them, spend time and make them feel worth something, I don't think we were put here to do what we are doing, our society is broken from the foundations up in hoping future generations will figure this out and lo e the world we live on and each other more no matter where we are from 😆
